#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.129"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.129:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.129:0.2"
msgid "13. Kusināravagga"
msgstr "13. Kusināra"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.129:0.3"
msgid "129. Paṭhamaanuruddhasutta"
msgstr "129. Anuruddha (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.129:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā anuruddho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā "
"anuruddho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Anuruddha went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

msgctxt "an3.129:1.2"
msgid ""
"“idhāhaṃ, bhante, dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena yebhuyyena "
"passāmi mātugāmaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ "
"nirayaṃ upapajjamānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Sometimes, sir, with my clairvoyance that’s purified and superhuman, I see "
"that females—when their body breaks up, after death—are mostly reborn in a "
"place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "an3.129:1.3"
msgid ""
"Katihi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"How many qualities do females have so that they’re reborn in a place of "
"loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.129:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Tīhi kho, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"“When they have three qualities females—when their body breaks up, after "
"death—are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "an3.129:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.129:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, anuruddha, mātugāmo pubbaṇhasamayaṃ maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā "
"agāraṃ ajjhāvasati, majjhanhikasamayaṃ issāpariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasati, sāyanhasamayaṃ kāmarāgapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""
"A female lives at home with a heart full of the stain of stinginess in the "
"morning, envy at midday, and sexual desire in the evening."

msgctxt "an3.129:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, anuruddha, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When they have these three qualities females—when their body breaks up, "
"after death—are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, "
"hell.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.129:2.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
